h1. countAll

h2. Purpose

{warning}
This method is deprecated. Use count() instead
{warning}

Counts all of the domain class instances for the specified query

h2. Examples

{code:java}
// count by query
Book.countAll([author:'Dan Brown'])
{code}

h2. Description

The basic syntax for the method is:

{code:java}
Book.countAll(Map query)
{code}

Parameters:

* @query@ - A "filter for querying":http://jkuehn.github.com/gorm-mongodb/guide/4.%20Querying.html

